  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>20230322</code> 经过重新排列后可以变为 <code>02320232</code>，这是将 <code>0232</code> 重复了 $2$ 次。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "像这样，只包含数字的字符串，如果通过适当的重新排列（也可以不变），能够变成某个字符串重复 $2$ 次的形式，我们称其为<strong>“开心串”</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定一个只包含数字的字符串 $S$，请你求出满足以下所有条件的整数对 $(l, r)$ 的个数。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$1 \\leq l \\leq r \\leq |S|$（$|S|$ 表示 $S$ 的长度）",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$S$ 的第 $l$ 个字符到第 $r$ 个字符组成的（连续的）子串是一个“开心串”",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "输入为以下格式，从标准输入读取。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "> $S$",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "请输出满足条件的整数对的个数。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "20230322",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "4",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$S =$ <code>20230322</code>。满足条件的整数对 $(l, r)$ 有 $(1,6), (1,8), (2,7), (7,8)$，共 $4$ 个。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "出现偶数次",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "题目要求子串中每个数字（0-9）都出现偶数次。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在数学逻辑上，“出现偶数次” 等同于：<strong>该数字出现的次数对 2 取模的结果为 0</strong>。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "状态压缩：用一个整数代表 10 个数字的奇偶性",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "既然我们只关心 0-9 这十个数字出现的<strong>奇偶性</strong>，我们可以用一个 <strong>10 位的二进制数</strong> 来表示当前前缀的状态：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "第 $k$ 位为 <code>0</code>：表示数字 $k$ 出现了偶数次。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "第 $k$ 位为 <code>1</code>：表示数字 $k$ 出现了奇数次。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "从区间到前缀",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "设 $PrefixMask[i]$ 为前 $i$ 个字符的状态。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于子串 $S[L, R]$，其内部数字 $k$ 的出现次数，等于 $PrefixMask[R]$ 的第 $k$ 位与 $PrefixMask[L-1]$ 的第 $k$ 位进行<strong>异或</strong>的结果。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "要使子串 $S[L, R]$ 中所有数字都出现偶数次，必须满足：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$PrefixMask[R] \\oplus PrefixMask[L-1] = 0$$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "即：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$PrefixMask[R] == PrefixMask[L-1]$$",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int cnt[2000];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tstring s; cin >> s;\n\tint n = s.size(); s = ' ' + s;\n\tll ans = 0, now = 0;\n\tcnt[now]++;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tnow ^= (1ll << (s[i] - '0'));\n\t\tans += cnt[now];\n\t\tcnt[now]++;\n\t}\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
